CHANGELOG — GreenLeaf Website  
This changelog documents the full development history of the GreenLeaf Website POE Project.  
Version numbers represent major updates, improvements, and fixes.



 — Initial Website Setup
- Created project structure and main pages (Home, About, Services, Gallery, Enquiry, Contact).
- Added basic navigation and placeholder content.
- Set up initial CSS file and linked pages.
- Added sample images and basic layout structure.



 — Layout & Styling Enhancements
- Improved typography for headings, body text, and buttons.
- Applied the GreenLeaf color scheme across all pages.
- Updated layout spacing, margins, and padding for a polished design.
- Adjusted responsive styling for mobile and tablet screens.



 — Feedback Fixes (From Part 2 Review)
- Corrected broken navigation links.
- Reorganized CSS using consistent naming and grouping.
- Improved image alt text to match accessibility guidelines.
- Fixed overlapping elements on smaller screen sizes.
- Updated inconsistent typography and spacing issues.



 Folder Structure & Documentation
- Reorganized project folder structure for clarity:
  - `/assets/css/`
  - `/assets/js/`
  - `/assets/images/`
- Removed unused files and images.
- Updated README with correct descriptions and structure.
- Fixed GitHub Pages live link issues.



 JavaScript Features Added
- Implemented accordion for FAQs.
- Added interactive Tabs on Services page.
- Added Modal popup for promotions/news.
- Implemented Lightbox for Gallery page.
- Added Search feature with real-time filtering.
- Added dynamic content (live date, footer year auto-update).



  Maps & Forms
- Added Google Interactive Map on Contact page.
- Implemented Enquiry Form with full JS validation:
  - Name, email, phone, message validation
  - User feedback messages
- Built Contact Form with:
  - JavaScript validation
  - Email sending functionality (EmailJS / backend)



 SEO Optimization
- Added meta title tags for all pages.
- Added meta descriptions and keywords.
- Improved image filenames for SEO.
- Added descriptive alt text for accessibility.



 Final Documentation Updates
- Updated README with:
  - Full project description  
  - Setup instructions  
  - Browser support  
  - Links (repo + live site)  
  - References  
- Completed CHANGELOG documentation.
- Tested website on multiple devices.



 Final Release
- All pages validated and tested.
- All JavaScript features tested.
- GitHub and Live website links verified.
- POE Project completed and ready for submission.
